Package quiver

Contains classes used in implementation of quiver, including classes representing vertices, arrows, and relations, along with methods for manipulation and rendering of quivers.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
QArrow arrows in a quiver
QCommutativityRelation represents commutativity relations in a quiver, i.e., relations of the form p1=p2, where p1, p2 are paths starting and ending at the same vertex.
QItem this is a base class for all items in a quiver, including points, arrows, and relations
QItemToIntegerMap maps items to integer values
QPath paths in a quiver
QPoint points (vertices) in a quiver.
Quiver represents quiver, and provides operations on and access to items contained in the quiver, including points (vertices), arrows, and relations
QUndoRedoAddedItem class for tracking items added to quiver
QUndoRedoDeletedItem class for tracking items deleted from quiver
QUndoRedoItem class for tracking items added to/deleted from quiver, for undo/redo this is used by the undo/redo mechanism
QUndoRedoMovedPoint class for tracking items deleted from quiver
QUndoRedoStack  
QZeroRelation zero relations - paths whose composition is zero
 

Package quiver Description

Contains classes used in implementation of quiver, including classes representing vertices, arrows, and relations, along with methods for manipulation and rendering of quivers.
